{"tid":359742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：閉路電視揭林子健安全上車離開旺角","createTime":"2017-08-14T17:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T04:43:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b99eddb302df6688b125c6a3ff11de9e7db11fab","tid":359742,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"民主黨黨員林子健聲稱上周四在旺角街頭被人擄走及毆打事件發生戲劇性發展據了解，林子健今日凌晨12時半在大角嘴其母寓所附近，被警方西九龍總區重案組以涉嫌誤導警務人員罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警員翻查當日附近的閉路電視，清楚顯示林子健安全上車離開旺角，所以昨晚深夜展開行動作出拘捕。警方掌握事態後，於周一晚上展開行動搜捕林，至凌晨12時半於林母大角嘴寓所附近將他拘捕，押返旺角警署，據了解稍後會將他押返馬鞍山家中蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨成員林子健早前報稱上周四在旺角街頭被擄走，並遭迷暈、禁錮和毆打，及用釘書機在大腿上釘上「十字架」形的21口釘，至翌日凌晨於一沙灘獲釋。"},{"pid":"6e975ccf827147446afd8b4f42a147d4394e7ca3","tid":359742,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:13:14.000Z","msg":",,,"},{"pid":"ac56a3edceafe453c7e88cbc4878df31261878ef","tid":359742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:55:53.000Z","msg":"安全上車離開旺角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8383152c5e70c4781f56c245fb0a4175804261a3","tid":359742,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"安全上車<br />\n成班炒車"},{"pid":"8bbbdd98264502938ba0d14155613b724c05225d","tid":359742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T03:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安全上車<br />\n成班炒車</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50006c4cb04eb7637278b4d1682de1e32ccb894d","tid":359742,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"仆街, 無豬黃絲敢入黎！"},{"pid":"a9ca538dddd7035e4f4a43a862cd3e93473c136c","tid":359742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T03:07:28.000Z","ms